	<p class="text">All Iperius Backup features are created to get the highest level of execution agility and ease of configuration. Iperius allows you to perform different backup types on many devices: NAS, RDX, LTO or DAT tapes, external USB drives, networked computers, FTP servers, Cloud storage services, such as Google Drive, Amazon S3, Azure Storage, Dropbox or OneDrive. Iperius can backup SQL Server, MySQL, MariaDB, PostgreSQL and Oracle databases and also make Drive Image backups, and create whole-disk images for Disaster Recovery and system bare metal restore with a few clicks. In addition you have many essential features such as e-mail notifications, detailed log files for each backup operation, execution of external processes and scripts, backup of open files (VSS), installation as service, synchronization, AES 256 bit encryption, Zip 64 compression, etc. ...</p>
